[06/07/2019 01:08:29] <font color="#ffff00">Tenga.</font>
[06/07/2019 01:08:31] <font color="#ffffff">Gracias.</font>
[06/07/2019 01:09:01] <font color="#ffffff">¿Qué, de miranda?</font>
